node.text: Photo by @mikemezphoto Into the night…photographing storms from sunset and through blue hour is by far my favorite time to shoot. The colors, textures…the way the ambient light reflects softly off the clouds and lightning illuminates the inside, it’s all so spectacular. This was one of the last looks I had at the Earth, Texas supercell this year as it gave us one heck of a view before the sky went dark. #place #nature #texas #planet #travel #tlpicks #supercell #worldshotz #superhubs #landscapes

node.text: Photo by @yensen_tan 🐍 Trimeresurus insularis 🐍 is a venomous pit viper subspecies found in Indonesia and East Timor. Common names include: white-lipped island pit viper, Lesser Sunda pit viper, and Sunda Island pit viper. Found in Indonesia on eastern Java, Bali, Lombok, Sumbawa, Sumba, Komodo, Rinca, Flores, Adonara, Lembata, Pantar, Alor, Roti, Semau, Timor, Wetar, Kisar and Romang.
